{"tid":2510890,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"咩話，做掌上壓可以幫到612","createTime":"2021-04-30T13:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T13:12:44.000Z","uid":94771,"like":31,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f951a8baea67679bd55fd1cd9118531b58d4d873","tid":2510890,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:00:25.000Z","msg":"<strong>又健到身同培養做運動習慣，又幫到612</strong><br />\n而612幫到有需要的手足<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>⚠️截止日期： 2021.05.02</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZFXWV43wNQR2D8vygoQu5A2gD1ZSKabNz1yPEak3msyw?filename=iXgVmso.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiXgVmso.jpg&h=0c81708a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcAjTFtW6GXsTr4v7ZpDMoFgCBfjch7i7oJxtAbG2bG6f?filename=qsHRaUS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqsHRaUS.jpg&h=ee14cc18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>詳情</ins><br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong>《DONATE 612 PUSH UP CHALLANGE》</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n💛參與資格：<br />\n<strong>- 香港人，可以拍片做掌上壓，有支持612基金嘅心</strong><br />\n<br />\n🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♂️參與方法：<br />\n<strong>- 出力：任何地方任何時間做掌上壓，拍片上載到內文網址 （Donate612 個人簡介有link可以直接咁入去😉）或傳送至IG INBOX</strong><br />\n<br />\n⚠️拍片注意事項：<br />\n-每段影片最少做20下掌上壓<br />\n-如在家中拍攝切勿暴露任何個人資料/居住環境<br />\n-必須將個人樣貌及明顯個人特徵隱藏，建議帶頭套/blockbloc/直接拍攝下半身<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n💰✅目標籌得掌上壓1500下，捐款HKD 15000<br />\n（作為一千分之一嘅力量💪🏻）<br />\n<br />\n歡迎每位同路人於截止日期前提交多段影片💛盡力而為將掌上壓培養成習慣🙌🏻<br />\nSource :<blockquote> <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tv/COF09jaj79_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftv%2FCOF09jaj79_%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=d6fa3c06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tv/COF09jaj79_/</a></blockquote><br />\n -------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"orange\">係聽日啦，聽日就到啦</span></strong></span><br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><strong>五一懲罰祭</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qme9ykqGEhqUHNetwcguybV7SnE7PBjMqNUZL6t69W55hc?filename=dXvOGva.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXvOGva.png&h=83829776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<ins>個Apps見到偷跑咗，有連登巴打POST咗出哩</ins><br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"large\"><strong>懲罰MEE 嘅app已經上架<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2510086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2510086</a></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong>【「黃圈未死！」 &mdash;&mdash; 五一懲罰祭！玩到十幾萬獎品？ 】</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n過去半年，香港的流行文化，從「樂壇已死」走到「樂壇不死」！<br />\n靠的不只是藝人，而是香港人。<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n過往這幾個月，每逢提到黃店 / 黃色經濟圈，聽到的似乎都是壞消息：有黃店再度告急，才能重見一兩天的人潮；有些黃店沒有選擇告急，唯有選擇默默結業。在疫情與政府打壓下，許多小店苦苦堅持，黃色經濟圈似乎失去了昔日的活力與力量。<br />\n-<br />\n香港樂壇，只要有香港人聽就永遠不死！<br />\n同樣，黃圈有香港人撐就永遠不死！<br />\n-<br />\n今次的五一懲罰祭，又有新玩法（留意我地個Page），而亦獎品總值更高達六位數字！！！！！💵💵💵<br />\n<br />\n今年的五一懲罰祭，將會進一步延長至五月九日，橫跨兩個週末，希望能夠同時透過母親節的效應，為黃店帶來更多營業額。<br />\n文宣Template👉 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2R3vj15\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2R3vj15&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=7525b624\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2R3vj15</a><br />\n（歡迎已收到確認信息的商戶下載使用）<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n登記表格<br />\n實體商戶👉 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/51week1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F51week1&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=6f1ea94c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/51week1</a><br />\n網店/非實體商戶👉 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/51week2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F51week2&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=2587de38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/51week2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"orange\"><ins>Source : <a href=\"https://t.me/punishC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FpunishC&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=5070a6a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/punishC</a>  </ins></span></strong></span><br />\n -------------------------------------------------------------------"},{"pid":"17f74ba37e96b0392aa09601fd70cbe644e704e7","tid":2510890,"uid":72466,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:00:29.000Z","msg":"so i say i love u"},{"pid":"1509d2fbdbc8ab0d35127c623d423aed54b3bcdf","tid":2510890,"uid":154490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:00:33.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"1873bce9e3c218d7762297276cc72a918da5202e","tid":2510890,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:00:36.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"b4770731d2e83a6daf54f9cd27c3d93bf3eb07ab","tid":2510890,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:00:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7db94500a69f676b2a427328c136be4f6b49f4","tid":2510890,"uid":72466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"612~~~"},{"pid":"8ad33b198462a5c6788d476bcc9a75801b5cc6d9","tid":2510890,"uid":72466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:00:52.000Z","msg":"啪"},{"pid":"9ed577f85da69cf793f880a723f4afdf4488b386","tid":2510890,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad98f1eb4c5621bfad0c2dafc105a2e5fffb4c5","tid":2510890,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i