f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9329e8ce314f72d0793c341eb451e3916c45d84","tid":2510890,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4753290693bac21e5239a2863564f0e396cb9651","tid":2510890,"uid":241131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:03:12.000Z","msg":"推！膝上壓得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:04:01.000Z","msg":"練下掌上壓la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9fffbe785bfd017b2aebe28c3dd234febfe7425","tid":2510890,"uid":67573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4753290693bac21e5239a2863564f0e396cb9651","tid":2510890,"uid":241131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:03:12.000Z","msg":"推！膝上壓得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:04:07.000Z","msg":"肯做已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809fcdb20d2bd873debbb8e214d1f6dabad87e8e","tid":2510890,"uid":209603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:04:10.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n【📕為在囚手足徵集16本書籍📙】<br />\n<br />\n我們正聯同天水連線及抗爭點滴為在囚手足徵集以下16本書本：<br />\n<br />\n1. 活出意義來──從集中營說到存在主義（已徵得）<br />\n2. 覺醒公民（已徵得）<br />\n3. 讚！日文初學20堂課1：從五十音進擊日文<br />\n4. 邊聽邊寫！簡單快速日文入門<br />\n5. 初學日文的第一堂課: 用康乃爾筆記法學日文<br />\n6. 一定要幸福喔！自己學也行的手相占卜<br />\n7. 開運 姓名判斷事典―姓名判斷、命名、改名が自分でできる!<br />\n8. 祕密三部曲套書：《The Secret 祕密》<br />\n9. 警國論（已徵得）<br />\n10. 要決心忘記 我便記不起 （鄭梓靈）<br />\n11. 低端中國：黨、土地、農民工，與中國即將到來的經濟危機（已徵得）<br />\n12. 萬獸寓言（劉銳紹）（已徵得）<br />\n13. 技術分析攻略（林瑞芬）<br />\n14. 記得你是誰：哈佛的最後一課（已徵得）<br />\n15. 反修例風暴採訪戰場<br />\n16. 平凡的邪惡 - 漢娜顎蘭<br />\n<br />\n如閣下能捐出，請務必先聯絡我們<br />\nTelegram: @swallowlife<br />\nFacebook: @swallowlife<br />\nInstagram: @swallowlife.hk<br />\n<br />\n圍牆上的圖書館旨在為在囚手足搜集各類書本、推介各個範疇高質書本以及定期製作書單予在囚手足挑選書本，並希望創造一個平台予香港人交流及搜集高質的書本，裝備思想、提升水平，留有用之身以待將來。<br />\n<br />\n圍牆上的圖書館<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swallowlife.org/圍牆上的圖書館\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swallowlife.org%2F%E5%9C%8D%E7%89%86%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%96%E6%9B%B8%E9%A4%A8&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=9a7379b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swallowlife.org/圍牆上的圖書館</a><br />\n<br />\n天水連線X抗爭點滴X燕子生命－寫信師計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swallowlife.org/intro-heartwithmate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swallowlife.org%2Fintro-heartwithmate&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=587d9cd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swallowlife.org/intro-heartwithmate</a>"},{"pid":"6d376bbd18d8e9d444f94225e0d29ffeca64809d","tid":2510890,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9329e8ce314f72d0793c341eb451e3916c45d84","tid":2510890,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4753290693bac21e5239a2863564f0e396cb9651","tid":2510890,"uid":241131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:03:12.000Z","msg":"推！膝上壓得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:04:01.000Z","msg":"練下掌上壓la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />掌上壓唔難啦下嗎"},{"pid":"11c12ccfc6986c003729ef925d50a5815747b61f","tid":2510890,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b4654f659ce824e