）<br />\n14. 記得你是誰：哈佛的最後一課（已徵得）<br />\n15. 反修例風暴採訪戰場<br />\n16. 平凡的邪惡 - 漢娜顎蘭<br />\n<br />\n如閣下能捐出，請務必先聯絡我們<br />\nTelegram: @swallowlife<br />\nFacebook: @swallowlife<br />\nInstagram: @swallowlife.hk<br />\n<br />\n圍牆上的圖書館旨在為在囚手足搜集各類書本、推介各個範疇高質書本以及定期製作書單予在囚手足挑選書本，並希望創造一個平台予香港人交流及搜集高質的書本，裝備思想、提升水平，留有用之身以待將來。<br />\n<br />\n圍牆上的圖書館<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swallowlife.org/圍牆上的圖書館\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swallowlife.org%2F%E5%9C%8D%E7%89%86%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%96%E6%9B%B8%E9%A4%A8&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=9a7379b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swallowlife.org/圍牆上的圖書館</a><br />\n<br />\n天水連線X抗爭點滴X燕子生命－寫信師計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swallowlife.org/intro-heartwithmate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swallowlife.org%2Fintro-heartwithmate&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=587d9cd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swallowlife.org/intro-heartwithmate</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:10:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169cefce6646c9ceaacba33734b5117988690697","tid":2510890,"uid":145736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6e921efa78a4b03c966c8fd8ed122946a6fa54","tid":2510890,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11c12ccfc6986c003729ef925d50a5815747b61f","tid":2510890,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b4654f659ce824e5775e53e4f5e97e106b3a3e4","tid":2510890,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:03:33